This paper discusses the challenges of incremental view maintenance for property graph queries, which is a topic related to database management systems (cs.DB). The approach presented in the paper uses nested relational algebra, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the implementation of the approach, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
